title: BRIEF-Molina Healthcare Reports Q1 Adj Shr $1.71
text:
April 30, 2018 / 10:55 AM / Updated 10 minutes ago BRIEF-Molina Healthcare Reports Q1 Adj Shr $1.71 Reuters Staff
April 30 (Reuters) - Molina Healthcare Inc:
* MOLINA HEALTHCARE ANNOUNCES FIRST QUARTER 2018 RESULTS AND INCREASES FISCAL YEAR 2018 GUIDANCE * Q1 EARNINGS PER SHARE $1.64
* Q1 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.77 — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* 2018 GUIDANCE INCREASED BY $1.00 PER DILUTED SHARE TO A RANGE OF $4.00-$4.50 NET INCOME PER DILUTED SHARE
* SEES 2018 ADJUSTED NET INCOME PER DILUTED SHARE $4.24-$4.74
* FY EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $4.43 — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
